column3: grandfather likes to be modern in his language
giving those who observe him a pronounced feeling of the utmost respect
she had your dark suit in greasy wash water all year
yet he still thinks as swiftly as ever
he slowly takes a short walk in the open air each day
twice each day he plays skillfully and with zest upon our small organ
the quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog
you wished to know all about my grandfather
i just try to do my best
both figures would go higher in later years
i tried to tell people in the community
all the big baseball players get traded
i feel i can play this weekend
they carried me off on the stretcher
bright sunshine shimmers on the ocean
we gathered shells on the beach
he will allow a rare lie
their house is grey and white
nothing is as offensive as ignorance
nothing is as offensive as innocence
she is thinner than i am
i looked up and noticed two old men
i was conscious all the time
one validated acts of school districts
jane may earn more money by working hard
the train approached the depot slowly
